fields.title: Simply Marrions
fields.description:
Simply Marrions is a software solutions company owned by me. The company aims to develop its own solutions to be used by the public and become a well known franchise for its outstanding (mobile / web / IOT) solutions.
Website built with Django and SQL database

fields.title: CompuTech
fields.description: A desktop retail application for selling computer parts to customers. Built using .NET and MySQL database.

fields.title: ADB Auto
fields.description: Retail applications simulating the ADB franchise, selling automotive parts to consumers. built with .NET and MySQL database

fields.title: Trimega Movies
fields.description:
Movies application running on an Angular framework with the IMDB API.

Watch all your favorite movies/series/anime as you wish, view every cast member involved in the film or series.

fields.title: Hospital Management System
fields.description: A desktop system catered for all hospital needs. From clients booking appointments to doctors managing clients and new ones. Manage all the hospitals in a region to changing employments from nurses to doctors and all its patients.

fields.title: Reservation
fields.description: A restaurant reservation system for its customers. Customers reserves a table on a particular date and select their prefers dish for the day.

fields.title: Wanted
fields.description: Know all about the worlds most wanted terrorist. Using the FBI most wanted API, the app reads the data and visualizes it to the user.

fields.title: Ingroove
fields.description: Event booking mobile application. Organize and manage all your events with a click of a button. Advertise, and showcase all of your events on a single screen to anyone and everyone.

fields.information: Having worked at Huawei as a telecommunications engineer (intern), I have grasped the required skills and understanding about telecommunications and and networking. From the planning stage to, building and development, and all the to maintenance and documentation.

2018 was a year to remember. During this year, one of my CS lectures inform me that he had signed me up for a skills competition, which at that time would be held in KZN. A competition in which the youth from all around South Africa would come together and showcase their skills in all fields. We would be trailed and tested to our limits only to get the best out of the best, and only then, the best out of each skill will be chosen to represent South Africa in the World Skills Competition that was held in Kazan, Russia 2019. This final stage tests us on an international level as all the countries bring fourth the best of the best they have. What an honor it was to be in the forefront of the battle field to wave the south African flag up high  with pride as South Africa's "Information Technology Software Solutions for Business" architect.
